{"tid":865031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再講填平維港！咁係廢左蓄洪池武功！！","createTime":"2018-10-16T16:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T20:50:39.000Z","uid":38255,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7acf8d414b6f267e61c3ec01035279e365016b44","tid":865031,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">跑馬地</span>一帶分別在二○○○、○六和○八年的暴雨中廣泛水浸，銅鑼灣立德里和摩利臣山道交界被渠務署納入水浸黑點之一。該署總工程師麥嘉為接受訪問時表示，要三管齊下，解決跑馬地一帶水浸問題。首先在上游截流，興建港島西雨水排放截流隧道；其次在下游加鋪雨水渠，兩者已動工；而最主要的招數是興建蓄洪池，在大雨期間收集雨水，<span style=\"color: red;\">然後排出維多利亞港</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上環雨水泵房</span>的具體運作是在接近海邊排水口的位置建造一個導流室，把從低窪地區收集到的雨水導流至地下蓄洪池；同一時間，導流室內的水閘會關上，阻止海水倒灌至上游的低漥地區。而6台安裝在泵房內的潛水泵可<span style=\"color: red;\">將在地下蓄洪池的雨水泵出維多利亞港。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/224540_e73ee4400ee05bdce26b710de8d9b780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F224540_e73ee4400ee05bdce26b710de8d9b780.jpg&h=b43e1dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且仲有其他污水渠雨水渠都係排出維港，填平維港將來市區唔使黃雨都水浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：雖然我覺得大家都係玩膠發悔氣，但驚有人真心覺得個維港係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c46cfa259955c30e02a2183bde15fd65207245","tid":865031,"uid":30476,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a92a8ec473082745942d68463d91176c8c936ed","tid":865031,"uid":69213,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a394bfd7de954240b274977130e82b09dcffb2dc","tid":865031,"uid":29081,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"維港填唔到嫁喇，google 吓《保護海港條例》"},{"pid":"08e556fb61840c61b45fc28bc784511e47c1f9a9","tid":865031,"uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6a92a8ec473082745942d68463d91176c8c936ed","tid":865031,"uid":69213,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"On9，你駁長左條排水渠，仲邊到夠fall 排水，有backwater effect頂返上黎架<br />\n<br />\n同埋drainage唔會叫「水管」ga"},{"pid":"ffab55535bbf4a8ea6fb5b3102e233c3548ec7ce","tid":865031,"uid":69213,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:20:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8f41e110bfa3c44a4dcb824aca0addbe4503a33","tid":865031,"uid":44323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08e556fb61840c61b45fc28bc784511e47c1f9a9","tid":865031,"uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6a92a8ec473082745942d68463d91176c8c936ed","tid":865031,"uid":69213,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"On9，你駁長左條排水渠，仲邊到夠fall 排水，有backwater effect頂返上黎架<br />\n<br />\n同埋drainage唔會叫「水管」ga"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"On9，求撚其加幾個泵同吸濕大笨象咪得，有成千鳩幾億整人肉運水系統都仲得呀"},{"pid":"98dbacd9566a59d274577c2b2c658c299df1c198","tid":865031,"uid":57844,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"連登仔上網9up 就叻，實際情況識閪咩"},{"pid":"3165ec9eaf715435d8a05bb4a9d3dd03db29675b","tid":865031,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9a268ed823f60565336e3f0c08cf244c0175e88","tid":865031,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3165ec9eaf715435d8a05bb4a9d3dd03db29675b","tid":865031,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b8f41e110bfa3c44a4dcb824aca0addbe4503a33","tid":865031,"uid":44323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1